data.description:
Welcome to 932 Cannock Street, Grovetown, GA 30813 - a stunning 4-bedroom, 2-bathroom all-brick one-level home that seamlessly blends comfort, style, and outdoor luxury. Boasting a saltwater pool and an inviting outdoor living space, this residence is the epitome of Southern charm. As you step into the home, a warm and welcoming foyer greets you, adorned with laminate wood flooring that gracefully extends through the dining room and into the spacious living room. The kitchen, a focal point of the home, overlooks the living room and features granite counters, ceramic tile flooring, Old World cabinets, a pantry, and stainless-steel appliances, including a refrigerator. The living room is a cozy retreat with a trey ceiling and a gas log fireplace, providing the perfect setting for relaxation and entertaining. The owner's bedroom offers a touch of elegance with its trey ceiling, while the attached owner's bath boasts a double vanity, a separate shower, and a walk-in closet, providing a private sanctuary. All three secondary bedrooms are generously sized and come equipped with walk-in closets, ensuring ample storage space for everyone. The hall bath features a double vanity and a private shower, offering convenience and comfort for family and guests. The highlight of this property is the incredible outdoor oasis - a 25 x 16 covered patio added in 2009, providing the ideal space for al fresco dining, entertaining, or simply enjoying the Georgia sunshine. The entire back yard is enclosed with a privacy fence, ensuring a sense of seclusion and security. For additional convenience, all outbuildings remain, offering practical storage solutions for tools, equipment, or hobbies. The shed is 20x12*.
This home is not just a residence; it's a lifestyle, combining modern amenities with timeless charm. Experience the best of Grovetown living at 932 Cannock Street - where every detail has been carefully curated to create a home that is as functional as it is beautiful. Don't miss the opportunity to make this property your own and enjoy the perfect blend of indoor comfort and outdoor serenity. 

P.S. The pool liner and steps, HVAC and the water heater were all installed in 2023. And all have transferable warranties for the buyer.

Showing Schedule: 24 Hour Notice on Weekdays, 8 Hour Notice on Weekends
